snippet.title: Crazy Frog's Dancing JAVA GAME (MediaPlazza 2004)
snippet.description:
"Crazy Frog's Dancing" is official Java game by MediaPlazza and eFusion. The game was aviable for purchase at Jamba website.

GAMEPLAY
Press the good button of your mobile when a number arrives in the bottom rectangle. Use 0 for the mega combo. The mega combo becomes aviable as soon as gauge is full. You can then destroy all the numbers on the screen.

TRIVIA
In-game sprites were made from The Annoying Thing animation.
On the Jamba website were similar dancing games with other Jamba mascots such as Sweety The Chick.
